            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 方法一 对 \\(f(x) = \\cos \\sqrt{|x|}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.232,
                0.923,
                0.292
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(\\lim_{x \\to 0} \\frac{f(x) - f(0)}{x} = \\lim_{x \\to 0} \\frac{\\cos \\sqrt{|x|} - 1}{x} = -\\frac{1}{2} \\lim_{x \\to 0} \\frac{|x|}{x}\\) 不存在，即 \\(f(x) = \\cos \\sqrt{|x|}\\) 在 \\(x = 0\\) 处不可导，应选(D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.1,
                0.297,
                0.169,
                0.312
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "方法二"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.317,
                0.921,
                0.392
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(f(x) = |x|\\sin |x|\\) 时，\\(f(x) - f(0) \\sim x^2, f(x)\\) 在 \\(x = 0\\) 处可导且导数为0，不选(A)；当 \\(f(x) = |x|\\sin \\sqrt{|x|}\\) 时，\\(f(x) - f(0) \\sim |x|^{\\frac{3}{2}}, f(x)\\) 在 \\(x = 0\\) 处可导且导数为0，不选(B)；"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.399,
                0.921,
                0.454
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(f(x) = \\cos |x|\\) 时，\\(f(x) - f(0) \\sim -\\frac{1}{2} x^2\\)，\\(f(x)\\) 在 \\(x = 0\\) 处可导且导数为 0，不选 (C)，应选 (D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.064,
                0.46,
                0.231,
                0.475
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【答案】 (B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.481,
                0.404,
                0.498
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 设切点为 \\((x_0, y_0, z_0)\\)，则"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.318,
                0.503,
                0.701,
                0.569
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l} z _ {0} = x _ {0} ^ {2} + y _ {0} ^ {2}, \\\\ (2 x _ {0}, 2 y _ {0}, - 1) \\cdot (1, - 1, 0) = 0, \\\\ (2 x _ {0}, 2 y _ {0}, - 1) \\cdot (x _ {0} - 1, y _ {0}, z _ {0}) = 0, \\end{array} \\right.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.101,
                0.574,
                0.353,
                0.638
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "解之得 \\(\\begin{cases} x_0 = 0, \\\\ y_0 = 0, \\\\ z_0 = 0, \\end{cases}\\) 或 \\(\\begin{cases} x_0 = 1, \\\\ y_0 = 1, \\\\ z_0 = 2, \\end{cases}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.099,
                0.643,
                0.586,
                0.66
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故所求切平面为 \\(z = 0\\) 或 \\(2x + 2y - z = 2\\). 应选(B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.666,
                0.231,
                0.682
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（3）【答案】 (B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.099,
                0.685,
                0.825,
                0.724
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\sum_{n = 0}^{\\infty}(-1)^{n}\\frac{2n + 3}{(2n + 1)!} = \\sum_{n = 0}^{\\infty}(-1)^{n}\\frac{1}{(2n)!} +2\\sum_{n = 0}^{\\infty}(-1)^{n}\\frac{1}{(2n + 1)!}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.38,
                0.727,
                0.542,
                0.743
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= \\cos 1 + 2 \\sin 1,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.102,
                0.749,
                0.19,
                0.765
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "应选（B）."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.77,
                0.232,
                0.787
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（4）【答案】 (C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.099,
                0.79,
                0.717,
                0.829
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(M = \\int_{-\\frac{\\pi}{2}}^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}}\\frac{(1 + x)^{2}}{1 + x^{2}}\\mathrm{d}x = \\int_{-\\frac{\\pi}{2}}^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}}\\left(1 + \\frac{2x}{1 + x^{2}}\\right)\\mathrm{d}x = \\int_{-\\frac{\\pi}{2}}^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}}\\mathrm{d}x = \\pi ,\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.102,
                0.834,
                0.562,
                0.868
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(-\\frac{\\pi}{2} \\leqslant x \\leqslant \\frac{\\pi}{2}\\) 时, \\(1 + \\sqrt{\\cos x} > 1 > \\frac{1 + x}{\\mathrm{e}^x}\\),"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.099,
                0.873,
                0.801,
                0.911
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(\\int_{-\\frac{\\pi}{2}}^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}}(1 + \\sqrt{\\cos x})\\mathrm{d}x > \\int_{-\\frac{\\pi}{2}}^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}}1\\mathrm{d}x > \\int_{-\\frac{\\pi}{2}}^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}}\\frac{1 + x}{\\mathrm{e}^x}\\mathrm{d}x\\) ，即 \\(K > M > N.\\) 应选(C)."
        }
    ],
