                0.446,
                0.511,
                0.504
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "取 \\(\\pmb {P} = \\left( \\begin{array}{lll}1 & -1 & 0\\\\ 0 & 1 & 0\\\\ 0 & 0 & 1 \\end{array} \\right)\\) ，则 \\(P^{-1} = \\left( \\begin{array}{lll}1 & 1 & 0\\\\ 0 & 1 & 0\\\\ 0 & 0 & 1 \\end{array} \\right),\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.117,
                0.512,
                0.896,
                0.571
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为 \\(P^{-1}\\left( \\begin{array}{lll}1 & 1 & -1\\\\ 0 & 1 & 1\\\\ 0 & 0 & 1 \\end{array} \\right)P = \\left( \\begin{array}{lll}1 & 1 & 0\\\\ 0 & 1 & 1\\\\ 0 & 0 & 1 \\end{array} \\right)\\) ，所以 \\(\\left( \\begin{array}{lll}1 & 1 & 0\\\\ 0 & 1 & 1\\\\ 0 & 0 & 1 \\end{array} \\right)\\) 与 \\(\\left( \\begin{array}{lll}1 & 1 & -1\\\\ 0 & 1 & 1\\\\ 0 & 0 & 1 \\end{array} \\right)\\) 相似，应选（A）."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.081,
                0.577,
                0.248,
                0.593
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（6）【答案】 （A）."
        },
        {
