        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.117,
                0.709,
                0.615,
                0.741
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\int_0^1 f(x)\\mathrm{d}x = \\int_1^2 f(x)\\mathrm{d}x = \\frac{1}{2}\\int_0^2 f(x)\\mathrm{d}x = 0.3,\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.117,
                0.747,
                0.893,
                0.779
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(P(X < 0) = \\int_{-\\infty}^{0} f(x) \\, \\mathrm{d}x = \\int_{-\\infty}^{1} f(x) \\, \\mathrm{d}x - \\int_{0}^{1} f(x) \\, \\mathrm{d}x = 0.5 - 0.3 = 0.2\\)，应选(A)."
        },
        {
