            "content": "（9）【答案】 -2."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.099,
                0.112,
                0.926,
                0.146
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】因为 \\(\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{1}{\\sin kx}\\cdot \\left(\\frac{1 - \\tan x}{1 + \\tan x} -1\\right) = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{1}{\\sin kx}\\cdot \\frac{-2\\tan x}{1 + \\tan x} = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{1}{kx}\\cdot \\frac{-2x}{1 + \\tan x} = -\\frac{2}{k},\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.102,
                0.15,
                0.51,
                0.19
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故 \\(\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\left(\\frac{1 - \\tan x}{1 + \\tan x}\\right)^{\\frac{1}{\\sin kx}} = \\mathrm{e}^{-\\frac{2}{k}} = \\mathrm{e}\\) 即 \\(k = -2\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.194,
                0.314,
                0.211
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(10)【答案】 \\(2(\\ln 2 - 1)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.11,
                0.214,
                0.429,
                0.233
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(f^{\\prime}(1) = (2^{x})^{\\prime}\\big|_{x = 1} = 2\\ln 2,\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.154,
                0.235,
                0.888,
                0.288
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} \\int_ {0} ^ {1} x f ^ {\\prime \\prime} (x) d x = \\int_ {0} ^ {1} x d f ^ {\\prime} (x) = x f ^ {\\prime} (x) \\left| _ {0} ^ {1} - \\int_ {0} ^ {1} f ^ {\\prime} (x) d x = f ^ {\\prime} (1) - f (1) + f (0) \\right. \\\\ = 2 \\ln 2 - 2 = 2 (\\ln 2 - 1). \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.065,
                0.292,
                0.259,
                0.309
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（11）【答案】 \\(i - k\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.111,
                0.312,
                0.851,
                0.391
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】rot \\(\\pmb {F}(1,1,0) = \\left| \\begin{array}{ccc}\\pmb {i} & \\pmb {j} & \\pmb {k}\\\\ \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial x} & \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial y} & \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial z}\\\\ xy & -yz & zx \\end{array} \\right|_{(1,1,0)} = (y\\pmb {i} - z\\pmb {j} - x\\pmb {k})\\bigg|_{(1,1,0)} = \\pmb {i} - \\pmb {k}.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.066,
                0.398,
                0.259,
                0.428
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(12)【答案】 \\(-\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.113,
                0.433,
                0.896,
                0.467
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\oint_{L}xy\\mathrm{d}s = \\frac{1}{3}\\oint_{L}(xy + yz + xz)\\mathrm{d}s = \\frac{1}{6}\\oint_{L}[(x + y + z)^{2} - (x^{2} + y^{2} + z^{2})]\\mathrm{d}s\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.251,
                0.472,
                0.436,
                0.505
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= - \\frac {1}{6} \\oint_ {L} d s = - \\frac {\\pi}{3}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.066,
                0.51,
                0.246,
                0.528
