            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（13）【答案】 -1."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.11,
                0.53,
                0.885,
                0.548
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1},\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2}\\) 是 \\(\\mathbf{A}\\) 的线性无关的特征向量，则 \\(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1},\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2}\\) 是 \\(A^2\\) 的线性无关的特征向量."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.113,
                0.552,
                0.921,
                0.591
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(A^2 (\\alpha_1 + \\alpha_2) = \\alpha_1 + \\alpha_2\\) ，得 \\(\\alpha_{1} + \\alpha_{2}\\) 也为 \\(A^2\\) 的特征向量，因此 \\(A^2\\) 有二重特征值 \\(\\lambda = 1\\) 因为 \\(\\mathbf{A}\\) 有两个不同的特征值，所以 \\(\\mathbf{A}\\) 的特征值为 \\(\\lambda_{1} = -1,\\lambda_{2} = 1\\) ，于是 \\(|\\textbf{A}| = -1\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.066,
                0.596,
                0.237,
                0.629
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(14)【答案】 \\(\\frac{1}{4}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.11,
                0.633,
                0.764,
                0.65
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】由 \\(BC = \\varnothing\\) ，得 \\(P(BC) = 0\\) ，因为 \\(ABC\\subset BC\\) ，所以 \\(P(ABC) = 0\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.113,
                0.653,
                0.891,
                0.763
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} P (A C \\mid A B \\cup C) = \\frac {P [ A C (A B \\cup C) ]}{P (A B \\cup C)} = \\frac {P [ (A B C) \\cup (A C) ]}{P (A B \\cup C)} = \\frac {P (A C)}{P (A B \\cup C)} \\\\ = \\frac {P (A) P (C)}{P (A) P (B) + P (C) - P (A B C)} = \\frac {\\frac {1}{2} P (C)}{\\frac {1}{2} \\times \\frac {1}{2} + P (C) - 0} = \\frac {1}{4}, \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.113,
                0.769,
                0.273,
                0.801
